These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
Beverage: juice, almond-milk
1. Beverage:almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
2. Beverage:juice is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice |

 #################################
 
